quran[5{c,v,t}:
2,270,"tum ne jo kuch bhi kharch kya ho aur jo Nazar bhi maani ho, Allah ko uss ka ilm hai, aur zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi"
2,271,"agar apne sadqat alania do, to yeh bhi acha hai, lekin agar chhupa kar haajat mandoon ko do, to yeh tumahray haq mein ziyada behtar hai tumhari bohat si buraiyan iss tarz amal se mehv ho jati hain aur jo kuch tum karte hue Allah ko bahar haal uss ki khabar hai"
2,272,"logon ko hadaayat bakhash dainay ki zimmay daari tum par nahi hai hadaayat to Allah hi jisay chahta hai bkhshta hai aur khairaat mein jo maal tum kharch karte ho woh tumahray apne liye bhala hai aakhir tum isi liye to kharch karte ho ke Allah ki Raza haasil ho to jo kuch maal tum khairaat mein kharch karo ge, is ka poora poora ajar tumhe diya jaye ga aur tumhari haq talfi hargiz nah hogi"
2,273,khaas tor par madad ke mustahiq woh tang dast log hain jo Allah ke kaam mein aisay ghar gay hain ke apni zaati ksb muaash ke liye zameen mein koi daud dhoop nahi kar saktay un ki khud daari dekh kar nawaqif aadmi gumaan karta hai ke yeh khush haal hain tum un ke cheharon se un ki androoni haalat pehchan satke ho magar woh aisay log nahi hain ke logon ke peechay par kar kuch mangeen unn ki eaanat mein jo kuch maal tum kharch karo ge woh Allah se posheeda nah rahay ga
2,274,jo lau g apne maal shab o roz khulay aur chupay kharch karte hain un ka ajar un ke Rab ke paas hai aur unn ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka maqam nahi
